name: Dumpster Fire

name: Squonk
effect: Be very careful when forming a Contract with Squonk. Making any sort of eye contact will result in it exploding into a puddle of tears.
description: If any opposing Caster cries tears, Squonk appreciates the sympathy and leaves the arena (place Squonk in the Afterlife).

name: Fomo
effect: The desperate owner of this PAGE buys every set, every promo, every partnership collaboration, and every Kickstarter project for Fear Of Missing Out.
description: I gotta have it, or my collection isn't complete... What if I don't have it all my friends do... I might die...

name: Jump Thru Hoops
effect: LGS retailers must Jump Thru Hoops to receive our product. Any Shenanigans will not be tolerated. Holders of this PAGE must shut up and do what they're told.
description: All LGS retailers must be benevolent, resilient, and unconditionally appreciative at all costs or be shunned.

name: Obtaining a Promo
effect: To receive this promo, holder of this PAGE had to visit our booth, scan QR code, take a photo at booth, share photo on social media, tag M in post, e-mail image to M, confirm address, contact support@M, re-confirm address again, prepay shipping, contact support@M three more times to finally receive this PAGE several months later.
description: Con Promos give fans the feeling that they're appreciated and they connect with the game, but not like this...

name: Men in Black Borders

description: Pretty please understand the risk of associating with this menace. Be Safe, Be Well & Have Fun.
